title: 01/17/22 DPS Hour 1 Super Wildcard Weekend
itunes:title: 01/17/22 DPS Hour 1 Super Wildcard Weekend
description:
In hour 1 the guys recap Super Wild Card Weekend and why it shows how tough it is to beat Elite QBs. The Cowboys beat themselves with costly penalties. And it seems Big Ben is the only one who hasn't announced his retirement.
